Paper: hep-th/0204076

Date: 2002-04-08

Title: Solutions of the boundary Yang-Baxter equation for arbitrary spin

Authors: G. W. Delius and Rafael I. Nepomechie

Comments: 10 pages, LaTeX, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A35 (2002) L341-L348

We use boundary quantum group symmetry to obtain recursion formulas whichdetermine nondiagonal solutions of the boundary Yang-Baxter equation(reflection equation) of the XXZ type for any spin j.